file.name: DATA.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: Osmosis Historical Data
  description: REST API to get the historical data for Osmosis
  version: 1.1.1
servers:
  - url: https://api.osmosis.zone/
    description: Osmosis Historical Data
paths:
  /health/v1/check:
    get:
      tags:
        - health
      summary: Check Health
      operationId: check_health
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /overview/v1/metrics:
    get:
      tags:
        - overview
      summary: Metrics
      operationId: metrics
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /overview/v1/message:
    get:
      tags:
        - overview
      summary: Message
      operationId: message
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /ibc/v1/info:
    get:
      tags:
        - ibc
      summary: Ibc Info
      description: List all existing paths that have been manually set up on the config
      operationId: ibc_info
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /ibc/v1/all:
    get:
      tags:
        - ibc
      summary: Ibc All
      description: |-
        List all existing paths with pending packets, last tx and since when (in minutes)
           
        optionnal: filter by dex
      operationId: ibc_all
      parameters:
        - required: false
          schema:
            title: Dex
            type: string
          name: dex
          in: query
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /ibc/v1/source/{source}/destination{destination}:
    get:
      tags:
        - ibc
      summary: Ibc Source Destination
      description: List chosen source and destination paths with pending packets, last tx and since when (in minutes) strictly superior to trigger option
      operationId: ibc_source_destination
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Source
            type: string
          name: source
          in: path
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Destination
            type: string
          name: destination
          in: path
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Minutes Trigger
            type: integer
          name: minutes_trigger
          in: query
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /ibc/v1/source/{source}:
    get:
      tags:
        - ibc
      summary: Ibc Source
      description: List chosen source paths with pending packets, last tx and since when (in minutes) strictly superior to trigger option
      operationId: ibc_source
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Source
            type: string
          name: source
          in: path
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Minutes Trigger
            type: integer
          name: minutes_trigger
          in: query
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /ibc/v1/destination/{destination}:
    get:
      tags:
        - ibc
      summary: Ibc Destination
      operationId: ibc_destination
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Destination
            type: string
          name: destination
          in: path
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Minutes Trigger
            type: integer
          name: minutes_trigger
          in: query
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /ibc/v1/raw:
    get:
      tags:
        - ibc
      summary: Ibc Raw
      operationId: ibc_raw
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /pairs/v1/summary:
    get:
      tags:
        - pairs
      summary: Pairs Summary
      operationId: pairs_summary
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /pairs/v1/historical/{pool_id}/chart:
    get:
      tags:
        - pairs
      summary: Pairs Historical Chart
      description: |-
        - **pool_id**: ID of pool to return
        - **asset_in**: First name asset of PAIR (ex for ATOM/USDT, asset_out=ATOM (symbol) or asset_out=ibc/1XX (denom))
        - **asset_out**: Second name asset of PAIR (ex for ATOM/USDT, asset_out=USDT (symbol) or asset_out=ibc/2XX (denom))
        - **range**: Range of historical Data (Available values : 7d, 1mo, 1y, all)
        - **asset_type**: Type of asset in asset_in and asset_out (Available values : symbol, denom)
      operationId: pairs_historical_chart
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Pool Id
            type: integer
          name: pool_id
          in: path
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Asset In
            type: string
          name: asset_in
          in: query
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Asset Out
            type: string
          name: asset_out
          in: query
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Range
            type: string
          name: range
          in: query
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Asset Type
            type: string
          name: asset_type
          in: query
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /pools/v2/all:
    get:
      tags:
        - pools
      summary: Pools All
      operationId: pools_all
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Low Liquidity
            type: boolean
          name: low_liquidity
          in: query
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /pools/v2/{pool_id}:
    get:
      tags:
        - pools
      summary: Pool By Id
      description: '- **pool_id**: ID of pool to return'
      operationId: pool_by_id
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Pool Id
            type: integer
          name: pool_id
          in: path
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /pools/v2/liquidity/{pool_id}/chart:
    get:
      tags:
        - pools
      summary: Liquidity By Pools
      operationId: liquidity_by_pools
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Pool Id
            type: integer
          name: pool_id
          in: path
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /pools/v2/volume/{pool_id}/chart:
    get:
      tags:
        - pools
      summary: Volume By Pools
      operationId: volume_by_pools
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Pool Id
            type: integer
          name: pool_id
          in: path
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /tokens/v2/all:
    get:
      tags:
        - tokens
      summary: Tokens All
      operationId: tokens_all
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /tokens/v2/mcap:
    get:
      tags:
        - tokens
      summary: Tokens Mcap
      operationId: tokens_mcap
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /tokens/v2/{symbol}:
    get:
      tags:
        - tokens
      summary: Tokens By Symbol
      operationId: tokens_by_symbol
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Symbol
            type: string
          name: symbol
          in: path
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /tokens/v2/historical/{symbol}/chart:
    get:
      tags:
        - tokens
      summary: Token Price Historical Chart V2
      description: |-
        - **symbol**: Symbol of token to return
        - **range**: Range of historical Data (Available values : 5,15,30,60,120,240,720,1440,10080,43800)
      operationId: token_price_historical_chart_v2
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Symbol
            type: string
          name: symbol
          in: path
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Tf
            type: integer
          name: tf
          in: query
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /tokens/v2/liquidity/{symbol}/chart:
    get:
      tags:
        - tokens
      summary: Liquidity By Tokens V2
      operationId: liquidity_by_tokens_v2
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Symbol
            type: string
          name: symbol
          in: path
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /tokens/v2/volume/{symbol}/chart:
    get:
      tags:
        - tokens
      summary: Volume By Tokens
      operationId: volume_by_tokens
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Symbol
            type: string
          name: symbol
          in: path
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /tokens/v2/price/{symbol}:
    get:
      tags:
        - tokens
      summary: Tokens Price
      description: |-
        Available tokens are:
        - ** SYMBOL : https://info.osmosis.zone/tokens**
      operationId: tokens_price
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Symbol
            type: string
          name: symbol
          in: path
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /tokens/v2/top/{type}:
    get:
      tags:
        - tokens
      summary: Tokens Top Gainers Or Losers
      description: 'type can be either ''gainers'' or ''losers'' '
      operationId: tokens_top_gainers_or_losers
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Type
            type: string
          name: type
          in: path
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /tokens/v2/count/{pool_id}:
    get:
      tags:
        - tokens
      summary: Tokens Count V2
      operationId: tokens_count_v2
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Pool Id
            type: integer
          name: pool_id
          in: path
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Range Start
            type: string
          name: range_start
          in: query
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Range Stop
            type: string
          name: range_stop
          in: query
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /tokens/v2/volume/global:
    get:
      tags:
        - tokens
      summary: Tokens Volume Global
      operationId: tokens_volume_global
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /tokens/v2/volume/coin/{symbol}/chart:
    get:
      tags:
        - tokens
      summary: Volume By Tokens Chart V2
      operationId: volume_by_tokens_chart_v2
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Symbol
            type: string
          name: symbol
          in: path
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /tokens/v2/volume/{pool_id}/coin/chart:
    get:
      tags:
        - tokens
      summary: Token Volume By Pool
      operationId: token_volume_by_pool
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Pool Id
            type: integer
          name: pool_id
          in: path
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /tokens/v2/dominance/all:
    get:
      tags:
        - tokens
      summary: Tokens Dominance
      description: '**REPLACE BY**: Nothing'
      operationId: tokens_dominance
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
      deprecated: true
  /liquidity/v2/historical/chart:
    get:
      tags:
        - liquidity
      summary: Liquidity Historical All Chart
      operationId: liquidity_historical_all_chart
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /volume/v2/historical/chart:
    get:
      tags:
        - volume
      summary: Volume Historical All Chart V2
      operationId: volume_historical_all_chart_v2
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /volume/v2/total:
    get:
      tags:
        - volume
      summary: Total Volume
      operationId: total_volume
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /fees/v1/total:
    get:
      tags:
        - fees
      summary: Fees Total
      description: 'total fees paid from all pools since beginning '
      operationId: fees_total
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /fees/v1/pools:
    get:
      tags:
        - fees
      summary: Fees Spent Pools All
      description: fees paid on 24h and 7d timeframe for all pools
      operationId: fees_spent_pools_all
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /fees/v1/{pool_id}:
    get:
      tags:
        - fees
      summary: Fees Spent Pool
      description: fees paid on 24h and 7d timeframe from a choosen pools
      operationId: fees_spent_pool
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Pool Id
            type: integer
          name: pool_id
          in: path
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /fees/v1/total/historical:
    get:
      tags:
        - fees
      summary: Fees Historical
      description: total fees historically paid daily since the beginning
      operationId: fees_historical
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /fees/v1/historical/{pool_id}:
    get:
      tags:
        - fees
      summary: Fees Historical Pool
      description: total fees historically paid daily since the beginning for a given pool
      operationId: fees_historical_pool
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Pool Id
            type: integer
          name: pool_id
          in: path
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /search/v1/supply/osmo:
    get:
      tags:
        - search
      summary: Search Amount Total Supply Osmo
      operationId: search_amount_total_supply_osmo
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
      deprecated: true
  /search/v1/denom:
    get:
      tags:
        - search
      summary: Search Denom By Given Symbol
      description: '- **symbol**: symbol to return in denom'
      operationId: search_denom_by_given_symbol
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Symbol
            type: string
          name: symbol
          in: query
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /search/v1/symbol:
    get:
      tags:
        - search
      summary: Search Symbol By Given Denom
      description: '- **denom**: denom to return in symbol'
      operationId: search_symbol_by_given_denom
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Denom
            type: string
          name: denom
          in: query
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /search/v1/exponent:
    get:
      tags:
        - search
      summary: Search Exponent By Given Symbol
      description: '- **symbol**: symbol to return is exponent'
      operationId: search_exponent_by_given_symbol
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Symbol
            type: string
          name: symbol
          in: query
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /apr/v2/staking:
    get:
      tags:
        - apr
      summary: Apr Staking Osmo
      operationId: apr_staking_osmo
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /apr/v2/all:
    get:
      tags:
        - apr
      summary: Apr All
      operationId: apr_all
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /apr/v2/{pool_id}:
    get:
      tags:
        - apr
      summary: Apr Per Pool Id
      operationId: apr_per_pool_id
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Pool Id
            type: integer
          name: pool_id
          in: path
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /supply/v1/osmo:
    get:
      tags:
        - supply
      summary: Supply Osmo
      operationId: supply_osmo
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /supply/v1/ion:
    get:
      tags:
        - supply
      summary: Supply Ion
      operationId: supply_ion
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
  /tradingview/v1/authorize:
    post:
      tags:
        - tradingview
      summary: Token
      operationId: token
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Body_token_tradingview_v1_authorize_post'
        required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
  /tradingview/v1/symbol_info:
    get:
      tags:
        - tradingview
      summary: Get Symbol Info
      operationId: get_symbol_info
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
      security:
        - OAuth2PasswordBearer: []
  /tradingview/v1/history:
    get:
      tags:
        - tradingview
      summary: Token Price Historical Chart V2
      operationId: token_price_historical_chart_v2
      parameters:
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Symbol
            type: string
          name: symbol
          in: query
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: To
            type: integer
          name: to
          in: query
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: Resolution
            type: string
          name: resolution
          in: query
        - required: true
          schema:
            title: From
            type: integer
          name: from
          in: query
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
        '422':
          description: Validation Error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError'
      security:
        - OAuth2PasswordBearer: []
  /tradingview/v1/streaming:
    get:
      tags:
        - tradingview
      summary: Streaming
      operationId: streaming
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
      security:
        - OAuth2PasswordBearer: []
components:
  schemas:
    Body_token_tradingview_v1_authorize_post:
      title: Body_token_tradingview_v1_authorize_post
      required:
        - login
        - password
      type: object
      properties:
        login:
          title: Login
          type: string
        password:
          title: Password
          type: string
        scope:
          title: Scope
          type: string
          default: ''
    HTTPValidationError:
      title: HTTPValidationError
      type: object
      properties:
        detail:
          title: Detail
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ValidationError'
    ValidationError:
      title: ValidationError
      required:
        - loc
        - msg
        - type
      type: object
      properties:
        loc:
          title: Location
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        msg:
          title: Message
          type: string
        type:
          title: Error Type
